
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import FeatureBlock from '../components/FeatureBlock.astro';
---
<Layout title="Insight Hunter Lite: Local First Privacy Focused Finance Software | Offline Runway Calculator">
  <head>
    <meta name="description" content="Insight Hunter Lite is local first privacy focused finance software with offline runway calculator, burn rate tracking, and secure cash flow insights for solo founders." />
    <meta name="keywords" content="local first finance software, privacy focused financial tool, offline runway calculator, secure startup finance app" />
  </head>

  <Hero />
  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2.2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Insight Hunter Lite is the premier local first privacy focused finance software, offering an offline runway calculator and secure financial tools for solo founders.</p>
    <p>This edition runs entirely on your machine, ensuring complete data privacy while offering automated P&L snapshots, burn rate and runway calculations, and basic cash flow tracking. New enhancements include real-time dashboards for key metrics, simple budgeting rules for recurring expenses, and one-click PDF exports of investor-ready reports, including basic balance sheets and unit economics overviews. Drawing from Compass, Lite now supports introductory natural language queries for strategic insights, such as operational speed assessments, all processed locally for autonomy and privacy.</p>
    <p>Enjoy introductory scenario planning for personal what-if questions, such as hiring impacts or expense adjustments, powered by lightweight local AI processing with continuous learning from user patterns.</p>
    <img src="/images/lite-mockup.png" alt="Lite real-time dashboard and reports" class="feature-image">
    <p>For seamless upgrades to advanced forecasting and integrations, explore Standard or Full editions. Company updates on Lite enhancements are available in the updates section.</p>
    <a href="#" class="cta" style="display:inline-block; margin:60px auto;">Download Lite Free</a>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <FeatureBlock title="Local AI Insights" text="Natural language queries provide instant answers on runway, burn rate, or expense trends directly from your local data, with Compass-inspired speed and autonomy." image="/images/ai-query-mockup.png" alt="Local AI query example" />
    <FeatureBlock title="Automated Basic Reports" text="Generate P&L statements, cash flow overviews, and simple forecasts offline for quick investor sharing, enhanced by real-time learning." image="/images/mobile-mockup.png" alt="Offline report exports" reverse />
  </section>
</Layout>




